This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with the creation of visual images. Additionally, the use of Deep Neural Networks suggests that it may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also discusses the similarities between artificial neural networks and biological vision, which suggests that it may belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category. Finally, the paper may also belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) category as it deals with the creation of artistic images.
